Initiates a terminal session for a pod in the given Deployment.

Usage:
  stack enter <pod> [container] [flags]

Flags:
  -f, --field strings      Field selector
  -h, --help               help for enter
  -l, --label strings      Label selector
  -n, --namespace string   Namespace
  -s, --shell string       Provide a target shell.

Global Flags:
  -r, --project_directory string     set the project directory of the stack (default ".")
      --stack_configuration string   set the name of the configuration file to be used (default ".stack-local")
